txt.en: You have participated in Yule Festival!

Every day there is something to do in Frostbluff.  Every day there is Yule!  Come and join everyone in Frostbluff and participate in one of the many Yule Festival events.  We have a Sack of Presents waiting for you.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000> NOTE: This quest will be removed from your quest log when the current festival ends. </rgb>
'Well done, friend!  Come and sit by the fire a moment.  You have earned this Sack of Presents for all your hard work today!\n\n'Come back tomorrow and we shall have more gifts for you!'
